{"word":"Mephibosheth","slug":"mephibosheth","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Mephibosheth</b> <a href=\"#/H4648\">H4648</a> <br/> 1. Son of Saul by Rizpah, whom David surrendered to the Gibeonites to be slain<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=21&verse=9'>2Sa 21:9</a><br/> 2. Son of Jonathan:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=4&verse=4'>2Sa 4:4</a> <br/> - Called Merib-Baal<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=8&verse=34'>1Ch 8:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=40'>1Ch 9:40</a> <br/> - Was lame<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=4&verse=4'>2Sa 4:4</a> <br/> - David entertains him at his table<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=9&verse=7'>2Sa 9:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=21&verse=7'>2Sa 21:7</a> <br/> - Property restored to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=9&verse=10'>2Sa 9:10</a> <br/> - His ingratitude to David at the time of Absalom's usurpation<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=16&verse=4'>2Sa 16:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=19&verse=30'>2Sa 19:30</a> <br/> - Property of, confiscated<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=16&verse=4'>2Sa 16:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=19&verse=30'>2Sa 19:30</a> "}]}